Uses of Package
edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model

  • Packages that use edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model 
    Package Description
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model
    Contains the DiscourseDB Core object model with the object relational mappings using Hibernate 4.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.annotation
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB Annotation Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.macro
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB Macro Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.system
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB System Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.user
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB User Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.annotation
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB annotation repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.annotation.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.system
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB system repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.system.
  • Classes in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model used by edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model 
    Class and Description
    BaseEntity
    Common subtype of all DiscourseDB entities
    TimedAnnotatableBE
    Adds basic fields to entities that keep track of their lifetime (Version, entity creation date, start date, end date)

    Adds basic common fields for type entities (Version, CreationDate, Type identifier)
